simple.util.tree

Class Node<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • simple.util.tree.Node<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - Type of the content.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<Node<T>>

    public class Node<T>
extends Object
implements Iterable<Node<T>>
    Simple node where all child nodes must contain the same content. Node names are determined by calling the content's toString method.
    Created: Oct 12, 2010
    Author:
    Kenneth Pierce
